                    data-url="https://www.nytimes.com/video/world/asia/100000002825241/india-at-a-crossroads.html?action=click&amp;contentCollection=world&amp;module=blog-video&amp;region=caption&amp;pgtype=article"
                    data-title="India at a Crossroads"
                    data-description="A journey across the worldâs largest democracy. This yearâs race between the Indian National Congress and the Bharatiya Janata Party reveals deep divisions in society and politics."
                    data-content-type="video">
                </div>
