<div id="sharetools-story" class="sharetools theme-classic sharetools-story" data-shares="email|Email,facebook|Share,twitter|Tweet,save|Save,show-all|More,ad" data-url="//learning.blogs.nytimes.com/2014/05/13/voting-for-change-india-goes-to-the-polls/" data-title="Voting for Change: Researching the Issues at Stake in India&#8217;s Election" data-description="In this lesson we explore the complex web of issues, history and culture behind the India vote. ">
